                     <interp inst="t18780211-237-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18780211-237-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp>Unlawfully uttering counterfeit coin.</rs>
